Title: Symmetry aspects of fermions coupled to torsion and electromagnetic

fieldsAuthors: J.L. Boldo and C.A.G. Sasaki

Comments: 9 pages, LaTex

Journal-ref: Europhys.Lett. 57 (2002) 180-185

We study and explore the symmetry properties of fermions coupled to dynamicaltorsion and electromagnetic fields. The stability of the theory upon radiativecorrections as well as the presence of anomalies are investigated.